    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/text/NumberFormat.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">java.text.NumberFormat</a>:</p>\n<pre><code>NumberFormat format = NumberFormat.getInstance(Locale.FRANCE);\nNumber number = format.parse(&quot;1,234&quot;);\ndouble d = number.doubleValue();\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Updated:</strong></p>\n<p>To support multi-language apps use:</p>\n<pre><code>NumberFormat format = NumberFormat.getInstance(Locale.getDefault());\n</code></pre>\n"
